<chapter><title>Latout Container Classes</title>
<indexterm><primary>Classes</primary>
<secondary>Layout Container</secondary></indexterm>

<para>These classes provide a method of grouping and presenting displayable widgets that is
independent of the underlying graphical subsystem. It allows windows which contain layout
containers to be resized without adverse problems to the widgets the widow contains. All
the widgets will retain their relative positions no matter what the size of the window.
</para>

