<!-- ********************************** -->

<section id="gtkalignment"><title>GTKAlignment</title>
<para>The GTKAlignment class is a subclass of the
GTKContainer class (<xref linkend="gtkcontainer" />).</para>

<para>This class controls the alignment of its child widget. A GTKAlignment widget should
